transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Haan ji sir, main Aasim bol raha tha India Mart se. Abhi meri baat hui thi na sir aapse. Main ye bol raha tha sir ye wala jo aapka number hai 74 aur last mein 783, ye aap hi ka number hai ya kisi aur ka number hai sir?
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Sir ye wala jo number hai jiske last mein 783 hai, ye aapka number hai ya kisi aur ka number hai?
Customer: Kaun sa sir?
Executive: Jiske last mein 783 hai, jiske last mein 783 hai sir.
Customer: Haan mera hi hai na sir, mera hi hai.
Executive: Wo dono same hi number, yani dono aap hi ke number hai ye sir?
Customer: Haan mere hi hai sir, mere hi hai.
Executive: Achcha. Achcha fir theek hai fir koi baat nahi. Maine isiliye aapse pucha kyunki us number se call aaya hua tha mere paas. To isiliye sir maine aapse pucha ke kahin aisa na ho ke maine aapse baat kari hai wo number kisi aur ka ho aur unko mere se baat karni ho sir.
Customer: Nahi nahi sir mera hi to wo check kar raha tha na check calling hoga hamara kal. Uske bare mein puch raha tha main. To uske bare mein na aur wo aapke paas mil gaya to jaldi.
Executive: Main samajh gaya. Haan haan.
Executive: Aapke paas sir. Aapke paas sir aapke.
Customer: Haan boliye. Haan boliye sir.
Executive: Main ye bol raha hu sir aapke paas feedback mail aayega to please waha positive feedback aap share kijiyega sir.
Customer: Haan theek hai.
Executive: Theek hai aapke paas mail mein aayega to positive feedback aap share kijiyega sir.
Customer: Theek hai.
